title: Saquon vs. McCaffrey, Lamar vs. Everyone, and More Week 16 Daily Decisions | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We highlight the high-priced players to bet big on, tell you why Lamar Jackson is worth it this week (and every week), and offer up some midrange players (7:20) before we help your wallet with the bargain bin players of the week and build our Week 16 daily fantasy lineups (29:35).
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
